  "3006280": {
    "name": "羊羊集合啦!（Sheepherds!）",
    "steam_appid": 3006280,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《羊羊集合啦！》（Sheepherds!）</strong> 是一款可供1到4人游玩的多人休闲合作游戏。在这款游戏中，玩家们将扮演调皮的牧羊犬，齐心协力引导羊群， 收集各种颜色的羊毛，并获得各种各样时尚装扮。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>征服羊群</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的羊群将会像真正的羊一样，小羊之间会相互跟随，并且相互影响。想当个合格的牧羊犬吗？那就得学会巧妙站位、试着与队友紧密合作，以及在关键时刻“汪”上一声！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然啦，你也可以随心所欲地做自己想做的事——总之，你只是一条小狗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/b8379e054322c1bbb2815ef74d679f19.poster.avif?t=1770365425\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/b8379e054322c1bbb2815ef74d679f19.webm?t=1770365425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/b8379e054322c1bbb2815ef74d679f19.mp4?t=1770365425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一款友好且轻松的合作游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合作意味着每个玩家都可以为共同的目标自由地作出贡献。没有任务的强制性分配， 没有集体压力， 没有时间限制——尽情享受，放心玩耍，你的每次行为都只会带来正向的反馈。和你的好朋友们友谊长存，避免“友尽”的风险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/2445faf65b0b83d441518ecf17f30ff7.poster.avif?t=1770365425\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/2445faf65b0b83d441518ecf17f30ff7.webm?t=1770365425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>量身定制你的牧羊节奏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为让大家都能享受最舒适的牧羊时光，还可自由调整难易度设置哦。如果你觉得小羊偶尔有点“太有主见”、暂时还摸不准节奏，也没关系——调整一下难度，让自己循序渐进、慢慢熟悉牧场的生活吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是初来乍到的小狗狗，还是经验丰富的老牧羊犬，都能找到最适合自己的快乐牧羊方式！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/4f9acf7be317a133846d8499f9cf3ff0.poster.avif?t=1770365425\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/4f9acf7be317a133846d8499f9cf3ff0.webm?t=1770365425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/4f9acf7be317a133846d8499f9cf3ff0.mp4?t=1770365425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用额外挑战来丰富你的游戏体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡的额外挑战会让游戏更有难度，在考验你的个人技巧与团队合作能力的同时，它们也会为游戏增添更深层次的乐趣。想要更刺激、更有参与感的玩法？这些任务一定会为你带来满满的成就感。别担心，如果你只想悠闲玩耍的话，也完全不用勉强哦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/68fd17259fbdb963865c0380e5de32f2.poster.avif?t=1770365425\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/68fd17259fbdb963865c0380e5de32f2.webm?t=1770365425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/68fd17259fbdb963865c0380e5de32f2.mp4?t=1770365425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>个性化打造你的专属狗狗形象</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把你辛苦得来的零食犒赏变成更多令人兴奋的奖品吧！快来解锁各种时尚的配饰、 五彩缤纷的服装、 独一无二的皮肤，让你的专属牧羊犬形象焕然一新。自由创造、随心混搭，打造出只属于你的萌趣造型，让它成为牧场里最闪亮的明星！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/b4d1e9ab910e51d0a32fc3b44517bd4e.poster.avif?t=1770365425\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/b4d1e9ab910e51d0a32fc3b44517bd4e.webm?t=1770365425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/b4d1e9ab910e51d0a32fc3b44517bd4e.mp4?t=1770365425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在广阔的牧场上放松身心</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在牧羊的间隙中忙里偷闲，休息片刻，享受生活中的小美好：与朋友拍照留念、阅读奶奶寄来的温馨信件，或体验她为你准备的各种欢乐小游戏。每解锁一个新区域，都会迎来全新的惊喜与更多的快乐时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/4cab31605822797190e9518f5e73ed04.poster.avif?t=1770365425\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/4cab31605822797190e9518f5e73ed04.webm?t=1770365425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/4cab31605822797190e9518f5e73ed04.mp4?t=1770365425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>狗狗全员到齐！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内目前共有18只可爱的狗狗品种，由你来随心选择：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006280/extras/14ccc9226e7d5db2552e6ab4053e6dad.avif?t=1770365425\" width=1080 height=608 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
